{"tid":1381944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好謝班後生仔","createTime":"2019-07-29T10:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:14:56.000Z","uid":104371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5239c97fc526a31a708f9cefe651f919797662c8","tid":1381944,"uid":104371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:56:07.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚去西營盤食完飯<br />\n撞正地鐵封站要行去上環坐<br />\n親眼見到條街全部都係D十幾歲 20頭後生仔女遊行<br />\n就係好感動又傷感<br />\n佢用拿把傘去對抗警棍，搵命博<br />\n俾差佬拉左分分鐘留案底<br />\n用自己前途去抵抗暴政，用行動去証明愛香港<br />\n條街仲殘留d催淚彈煙，自己行過都標眼水<br />\n咁岩條街到有個阿媽拖住個細路仔<br />\n佢地好心地叫家長好好保護細路仔，小心催淚煙<br />\n點知俾個家長吊返轉頭多得佢地搞事（心唸唔係有佢地你地個個已經隨時可以送中啦吊）<br />\n又見到個反方向路人隨手將手上把傘遞俾個示威者，個動作好自然，以示支持佢地<br />\n個時差唔多散水行過老麥<br />\n見到個個後生坐係門口食老麥<br />\n見到佢地樣真係好靚好單純相由心生<br />\n唸都唔會唸到一個讀緊書會自發上街遊行<br />\n正常社會以佢地咁o既年紀係唔應該會出現係哩到<br />\n宜家社會欠左佢地，我都欠左佢地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc4be9b11cc8bb5df5710e806a91c3773497f20d","tid":1381944,"uid":228296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:59:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ccb530a908ef417cba7a1fc66369706b6d83a9c6","tid":1381944,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:00:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7160dbce32f65639d1b7ec4491001765ad4d1cb7","tid":1381944,"uid":229019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX7EMKA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX7EMKA.jpg&h=990f4b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aEiXypB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaEiXypB.jpg&h=020f3ad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ans9pwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAns9pwg.png&h=b8d6d814&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a0d3b6a973f032af23bb301c2e5bcceff9b3de5","tid":1381944,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{